[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0829","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0829.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0566","title":"IBM AIX syslog 日志填充拒绝服务漏洞","description":"IBM AIX 系统中的 syslog 组件存在日志写入权限缺陷，攻击者可从任意位置向 syslog 文件写入大量日志条目，导致磁盘空间被占满从而引发拒绝服务。同时，恶意日志会淹没正常审计记录，掩盖攻击者的操作痕迹，增加安全检测与溯源难度。该漏洞影响 IBM AIX 操作系统，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0566"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-08-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:39.053","remediation":"升级 IBM AIX 至 4.3.3 或更高版本，安装 APAR IX87386 补丁。同时配置 syslogd 限制远程写入（修改 /etc/syslog.conf 禁用非必要远程日志接收），在 /etc/hosts.allow 中限制 syslog 端口（UDP 514）的访问来源，并启用日志轮转（logrotate）防止单一日志文件过大导致磁盘写满。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0566","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/c8abbfc77cc703e2fd85623576b0f07a0c8427eb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0566.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0566","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/ce91429859b5110820b1d31a41b0b1a3c67d9603/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0566.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0566.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24ebb1752fdaa57c8d421b21085e47d359e1300e/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0566.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-7cvc-2mx4-55wc/GHSA-7cvc-2mx4-55wc.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0566.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154400_154500.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--8aeb4aa9-e098-4c64-a9a7-a80928b5b3b8.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0829.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0498","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0498.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0301","title":"SunOS/Solaris ps 命令缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"SunOS 和 Solaris 系统中的 ps 命令存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。本地攻击者可通过向 ps 命令传递特制参数触发缓冲区溢出，从而获取 root 权限，实现完全控制目标系统。该漏洞影响 SunOS 5.3/5.4/5.5/5.5.1 及 Solaris 2.3/2.4/2.5/2.5.1 等多个版本。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0301"],"sources":["cve","exploitdb"],"published":"1997-08-01","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"建议升级到不受影响的 SunOS/Solaris 版本，或安装 Sun 安全公告 149 号提供的补丁程序。限制本地用户对 ps 命令的访问权限可缓解风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T12:06:30.705882439+00:00","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/149"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0498.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0268","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0268.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0122","title":"IBM AIX lchangelv 本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"IBM AIX 4.2 系统中的 /usr/sbin/lchangelv 工具存在本地缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地攻击者可利用该漏洞以 root 权限执行任意代码。攻击者需要通过本地账户登录系统，向 lchangelv 程序提交特制的超长参数触发缓冲区溢出，从而覆盖返回地址或函数指针劫持进程控制流。该漏洞影响 IBM AIX 4.2 版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高，攻击前提是拥有本地 shell 访问权限。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0122"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-07-21T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:38.147","remediation":"IBM AIX 4.2 用户应立即升级至 AIX 4.3.3 或更高版本，该漏洞已在后续版本中修复；或安装对应 APAR 补丁包。临时缓解措施：以 root 权限执行 `chmod 500 /usr/sbin/lchangelv` 移除 setuid 位，限制普通用户执行该程序。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-199