ublished":"1997-07-21T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:59.740","remediation":"升级 INN 至 2.0 或更高版本，该漏洞在 INN 1.7 及后续版本中已被修复。如无法升级，可在 innd 配置中限制 nnrpd 服务的远程访问来源 IP，或禁用 nnrpd 的远程连接功能作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.nai.com/nai_labs/asp_set/advisory/17_inn_avd.asp","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1443","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0247.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0247.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0247","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0247.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0247.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0247.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-69m7-6fwc-hxpx/GHSA-69m7-6fwc-hxpx.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/I/inn.nasl","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0432.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0080","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0080.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0025","title":"SGI IRIX df 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"SGI IRIX 6.3 系统中的 df 命令存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地攻击者可通过向 df 命令传入特制的超长参数触发缓冲区溢出，覆盖返回地址后执行任意代码，从而获取 root 权限。该漏洞影响 SGI IRIX 6.3 版本，利用条件是攻击者需拥有本地系统访问权限，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0025"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-07-16T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:22.730","remediation":"安装 SGI 提供的 IRIX 安全补丁 19970505-02-PX，升级到已修复的 IRIX 版本。如无法立即打补丁，可执行 `chmod u-s /usr/sbin/df` 移除 df 的 setuid 权限作为临时缓解措施，或使用 AUSCERT 提供的 overflow_wrapper 工具限制命令行参数长度（建议 MAXARGLEN=32）并记录异常调用。由于 SGI IRIX 已停止维护，建议迁移至受支持的现代操作系统。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.cert.org/advisories/CA-1997-21.html","http://www.kb.cert.org/vuls/id/20851","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/346","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/440","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19274","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/dc83b9e6d88de194a14e3020b4e71ac42054e609/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0025.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0025","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0025.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0025.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/04a84e78299e2aeaab4d2594fc26f920778c7b06/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0025.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-5wr5-299q-993r/GHSA-5wr5-299q-993r.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/kabaneridev/pt-notes/blob/05dba1a6e7d619d374878b2366ccc58b8e4a5ef2/CPTS-PREP/remote-management/linux-remote-protocols.md","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154400_154500.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0080.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0082","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0082.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0026","title":"SGI IRIX pset 命令缓冲区溢出本地权限提升漏洞","description":"SGI IRIX 6.3 系统中的 pset 命令存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地攻击者可通过向该命令提交特制输入触发缓冲区溢出，从而获取 root 权限。该漏洞需要攻击者拥有本地系统访问权限，利用门槛较低，成功利用后可完全控制受影响系统。CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0026"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-07-16T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:22.857","remediation":"立即升级到 IRIX 6.5 及以上版本（该系列已修复此漏洞）；如无法升级，可移除 /usr/sbin/pset 的 setuid 位作为临时缓解措施，执行 chmod u-s /usr/sbin/pset 禁止普通用户提权；严格限制本地用户的交互式 shell 访问权限，仅允许受信用户登录。由于 SGI IRIX 已于 2006 年终止支持且厂商已破产，建议将关键业务系统迁移到仍受支持的操作系统平台。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0026","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19347","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/dc83b9e6d88de194a14e3020b4e71ac42054e609/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0026.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0026","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0026.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0026.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/04a84e78299e2aeaab4d2594fc26f920778c7b06/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0026.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-jgjp-7pvm-43jq/GHSA-jgjp-7pvm-43jq.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50a