_at":"2026-07-12T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0028"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0091.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0092","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0092.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0030","title":"SGI IRIX xlock 命令缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"SGI IRIX 系统及其他类 Unix 操作系统（包括 BSD/OS、DG/UX、Debian、HP-UX、IBM AIX、Solaris）中 xlock 屏幕锁定程序存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。本地攻击者可利用该漏洞向 xlock 发送特制输入数据触发缓冲区溢出，从而获取 root 权限。该漏洞影响广泛的多款 Unix 操作系统，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0030"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-07-16T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:23.497","remediation":"SGI IRIX 系统应立即升级 xlock 程序至厂商已修复版本（如 IRIX 6.4 对应安全补丁），其他受影响系统（BSD/OS 2.1、Debian 1.3、HP-UX 10.34、IBM AIX 4.2、Solaris 2.5.1 等）应从各自厂商获取 xlock 安全更新。若无法立即打补丁，作为临时缓解措施可移除 xlock 的 setuid root 权限位（执行 chmod u-s /usr/bin/X11/xlock），限制本地用户以提权方式运行 xlock 程序。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0030"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0092.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0299","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0299.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0146","title":"NCSA httpd campas CGI 远程命令执行漏洞","description":"NCSA httpd 服务器自带的 campas CGI 程序未对用户输入进行充分过滤，远程攻击者可通过在查询字符串中插入编码的回车符（CR）注入任意系统命令，进而读取服务器上的敏感文件（如密码文件）或执行其他恶意操作。该漏洞影响多个版本的 NCSA web 服务器，无需身份认证即可远程利用，危害严重。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0146"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-07-15T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:41.800","remediation":"删除 cgi-bin 目录下的 campas 示例脚本，或确保 NCSA httpd 已升级至不受影响的版本。建议迁移至长期维护的 Web 服务器（如 Apache HTTP Server），并移除所有示例 CGI 脚本以避免类似安全问题。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1975","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/298","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20423","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab669d9fb37e52ed0619cb2b8265d34528fbe875/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0146.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0146","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0146.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0146.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0146.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-c22c-6v4p-99rm/GHSA-c22c-6v4p-99rm.json","https://github.com/NetBSD/pkgsrc-wip/blob/9e4b769742ed57395763142c26029c2f9910f15b/sara/PLIST","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/sid-msg.map","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/Freem93/grammar_nasl_v2/blob/63834ebb8cd6e97050e155291c7500ad53bb20c6/plugins/campas.nasl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0299.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0150","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0150.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0059","title":"SGI IRIX fam 服务信息泄露漏洞","description":"SGI IRIX 操作系统的 fam（File Alteration Monitor）服务存在信息泄露漏洞，攻击者无需身份认证即可通过远程网络请求获取目标服务器上的所有文件列表，导致系统敏感文件路径与结构暴露。该漏洞影响 IRIX 多个版本，CVSS 评分 7.3，危害等级高危，攻击者可借此进行信息收集，为后续针对性攻击创造条件。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.3,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0059"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-07-14T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:28.837","remediation":"立即安装 SGI 1997 年发布的安全补丁（SGI 安全公告 19970701-01-P），或升级 IRIX 至不受影响的更高版本。若无法打补丁，在 `/etc/inetd.conf` 中注释 fam 服务行并重启 inetd，或执行 `/etc/init.d/fam stop` 停止 fam 服务，再通过 `chkconfig fam off` 禁止开机自启。同时建议在边界防火墙上阻断对 fam 默认端口（TCP 9751）的外部访问。由于 SGI IRIX 已于 2006 年停止技术支持，建议将业务迁移至仍在安全维护期的操作系统。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/164","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/353","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/325"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0150.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0351","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0351.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0176","title":"WEBgais 1.0 远程命令执行漏洞","description":"WEBgais 1.0 存在远程命令执行漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过向服务器发送特制的 HTTP 请求，利用程序未对用户输入进行有效过滤的缺陷，在目标系统上执行任意命令，从而完全控制受影响的服务器。该漏洞影响 WEBgais 1.0 版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0176"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-07-10T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:45.797","remediation":"立即从 Web 服务器 cgi-bin 目录中删除 webgais 脚本或将其移除，同时检查服务器上是否存在其他无用 CGI 程序并一并清理。如业务必须使用该功能，应迁移至有安全维护的替代方案（如现代 Web 框架实现的文件搜索功能），并在 Web 服务器（Apache/Nginx）层面限制 CGI 执行权限。临时缓解措施可配置 Web 服务器 ACL 仅允许可信 IP 访问 CGI 目录。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0176","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20463","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/269e5b2b6ea60fdb4a03411be38d3e381b26e4c4/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0176.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0176","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0176.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0176.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0176.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/webgais.nasl","https://github.com/NetBSD/pkgsrc-wip/blob/9e4b769742ed57395763142c26029c2f9910f15b/sara/PLIST","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/1b69cf2313f68e29acceed58f52f6109cd37bb04/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-01xx/CVE-1999-0176.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/slacker247/GPDA/blob/fa9006d0877a691f1ddffe88799c844a3e8a669a/Sodi/Run/IDSrules/rule.840"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0351.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0351.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0351.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0093","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0093.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0031","title":"Microsoft Internet Explorer JavaScript 信息泄露漏洞","description":"JavaScript 同源策略绕过漏洞存在于 Internet Explorer 3.x/4.x 及 Netscape 2.x/3.x/4.x 等早期浏览器中。远程攻击者可通过在恶意网页中植入特制 JavaScript 代码，监控用户跨站点的网页浏览活动，窃取用户的浏览历史与访问行为等敏感信息。该漏洞由贝尔实验室发现并报告，CVSS 评分 2.6，危害等级低，但由于浏览器版本较早且已停止支持，实际利用价值有限。","severity":"LOW","score":2.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0031"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-07-08T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:23.630","remediation":"立即停止使用 Internet Explorer 3.x/4.x 及 Netscape 2.x/3.x/4.x，升级到受支持的主流浏览器（如 Chrome、Edge、Firefox 最新版本），这些浏览器已不存在该跨域脚本监控漏洞。对于无法升级浏览器的老旧系统，建议在终端安装脚本拦截插件（如 NoScript）并禁用 JavaScript 执行作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.codetalker.com/advisories/vendor/hp/hpsbux9707-065.html"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0093.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0378","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0378.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0196","title":"WEBgais websendmail 远程命令执行漏洞","description":"Webgais 1.0 的 websendmail 组件在处理 receiver 参数（$VAR_receiver 变量）时存在输入验证缺陷，远程攻击者可通过向目标服务发送特制 HTTP 请求注入系统命令，从而实现任意文件读取与远程命令执行。该漏洞无需身份认证，攻击条件低，CVSS 评分 5.0，影响运行 Webgais 1.0 的服务器系统。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0196"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-07-08T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:53.363","remediation":"立即删除 Web 服务器 cgi-bin/ 目录下的 websendmail 和 webgais 脚本，或通过 Apache 的 Directory 指令拒绝访问该 CGI 路径。WEBgais 1.0 已不再维护，无法通过升级修复。如必须使用，须在接收 $VAR_receiver 参数后过滤 shell 元字符（;、`、|、$ 等），并改用 Perl Mail::Sendmail 模块替代 open() 管道方式调用 sendmail。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/237","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/2077","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20483","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/92d64b4c9b3c5a0ce1fd1e5f8c017b9772e0139b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0196.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0196","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0196.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0196.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/db45dbc75ff0264d63b603291e4a83d7361bd7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0196.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/websendmail.nasl","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/79c2cf4630fcc44f2632735de08432a07cfaf204/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-35m5-388q-jrx8/GHSA-35m5-388q-jrx8.json","https://github.com/slacker247/GPDA/blob/fa9006d0877a691f1ddffe88799c844a3e8a669a/Sodi/Run/IDSrules/rule.820","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0196.json","https://github.com/jdkoftinoff/mb-linux-msli/blob/8adb103e34af9ff1d8d122e9ee2a1808836f0a14/uClinux-dist/user/snort/drop-rules/sid-msg.map"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0378.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0378.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0378.toml"}]